Theorem (interopen):
  for all v0, (for all v1, (if v0 is a subset of INT and v1 is a subset of INT and (v0 is open and v1 is open) then (the intersection of v0 and v1 is a subset of INT and the intersection of v0 and v1 is open)))
Proof:
